room_title: Escape room "The Cabin" by Deadbolt - Boneyfiddle Escape Rooms and Mysteries in Portsmouth (OH)
room_description:
You and your friends are hiking in the Shawnee State Forest around dusk. You find yourselves on a path you are unfamiliar with. You notice a cabin up ahead and decide to stop. The door is open so you wonder inside...
BAM, the door shuts behind you. You are locked in! You need to find a way out before “they” come home...
